; Sunsworn Chapel - Paladin intro arena.
; Stone castle chapel with watch towers and twin colonnades. White
; banners, holy braziers, altar at the north end. Mini-boss: Siege Master.
; This is the medieval/castle aesthetic Bond pulled OUT of Sword-Vow Ruins
; so that one could go full Japanese sakura grove.

